  "body": "Line 74 of the Crowdsale.sol file has:\r\n\r\n`    uint256 tokens = weiAmount.mul(rate);`\r\n\r\nShouldn't that instead be:\r\n\r\n`    uint256 tokens = weiAmount.div(rate);`\r\n\r\nIf it takes 1000 wei to buy a token, the number of tokens to issue/mint would be the number of wei sent to buyTokens() divided by the rate.  Right?\r\n\r\nHoping someone (else) can double check this.",
